Configuration Files:


MoGridLog4j.xml: 
> Logging configuration file for log4j.
CHANGE the path of all lines <param name="File" value=<MOGRID_HOME/logs/...>
Example: 
   <param name="File"
   value=/usr/MoGrid/logs/MobileGridLogger.log"/>


DiscoveryProtocol.properties:
CONTENT:
coordination.address: broadcast or multicast address for P2PDP comunnication channel
coordination.port:    P2PDP comunnication channel port
coordination.scan:    scan interval in milliseconds for P2PDP comunnication channel listen for new messages

DiscoveryProtocol.properties.broadcast: 
> Example of DiscoveryProtocol.properties file to broadcast

DiscoveryProtocol.properties.multicast: 
> Example of DiscoveryProtocol.properties file to multicast


ContextListener.properties: 
> Context Listener (CL) configuration file. The CL listen monitor service to free CPU and memory values.
CONTENT:
monitor.port: context listener port
monitor.scan: scan interval in milliseconds to listener for new monitor service info



